[mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet. Lovovertr\u00e6delse kan straffes med b\u00f8de.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Med venlig hilsen&nbsp;\/Best regards<\/span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Jeanette Frederiksen<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:maroon\">ERHVERVSSTYRELSEN<\/span><\/strong><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Langelinie All\u00e9 17<br>&nbsp;1780 K\u00f8benhavn \u00d8<br>&nbsp;Telefon: &#43;45 3529 1000<br>&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.erst.dk\/\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;color:black\">www.erst.dk<\/span><\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">ERHVERVS- OG V\u00c6KSTMINISTERIET<br>&nbsp;<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\">P<\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:green\">Pas p\u00e5 milj\u00f8et - udskriv kun denne e-mail hvis det er n\u00f8dvendigt<\/span><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;<\/span><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><\/body><\/html>","type":"html","stripped_images":[],"embedded_images":[],"options":{"strip-embedded":true}},"priorityId":null,"attachments":[]}

<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody><\/table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            <\/td>\r\n        <\/tr>\r\n    <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/td>\r\n                                        <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY \/\/ -->\r\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;min-width: 100%;background-color: #12171b;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bodyContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet.           <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet. Lovovertr\u00e6delse kan straffes med b\u00f8de.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Med venlig hilsen&nbsp;\/Best regards<\/span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Jeanette Frederiksen<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:maroon\">ERHVERVSSTYRELSEN<\/span><\/strong><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Langelinie All\u00e9 17<br>&nbsp;1780 K\u00f8benhavn \u00d8<br>&nbsp;Telefon: &#43;45 3529 1000<br>&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.erst.dk\/\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;color:black\">www.erst.dk<\/span><\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">ERHVERVS- OG V\u00c6KSTMINISTERIET<br>&nbsp;<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\">P<\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:green\">Pas p\u00e5 milj\u00f8et - udskriv kun denne e-mail hvis det er n\u00f8dvendigt<\/span><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;<\/span><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><\/body><\/html>","type":"html","stripped_images":[],"embedded_images":[],"options":{"strip-embedded":true}},"priorityId":null,"attachments":[]}

<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody><\/table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            <\/td>\r\n        <\/tr>\r\n    <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/td>\r\n                                        <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY \/\/ -->\r\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;min-width: 100%;background-color: #12171b;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bodyContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet.           <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet. Lovovertr\u00e6delse kan straffes med b\u00f8de.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Med venlig hilsen&nbsp;\/Best regards<\/span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Jeanette Frederiksen<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:maroon\">ERHVERVSSTYRELSEN<\/span><\/strong><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Langelinie All\u00e9 17<br>&nbsp;1780 K\u00f8benhavn \u00d8<br>&nbsp;Telefon: &#43;45 3529 1000<br>&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.erst.dk\/\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;color:black\">www.erst.dk<\/span><\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">ERHVERVS- OG V\u00c6KSTMINISTERIET<br>&nbsp;<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\">P<\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:green\">Pas p\u00e5 milj\u00f8et - udskriv kun denne e-mail hvis det er n\u00f8dvendigt<\/span><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;<\/span><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><\/body><\/html>","type":"html","stripped_images":[],"embedded_images":[],"options":{"strip-embedded":true}},"priorityId":null,"attachments":[]}

<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody><\/table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            <\/td>\r\n        <\/tr>\r\n    <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/td>\r\n                                        <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY \/\/ -->\r\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;min-width: 100%;background-color: #12171b;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bodyContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet.           <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet. Lovovertr\u00e6delse kan straffes med b\u00f8de.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Med venlig hilsen&nbsp;\/Best regards<\/span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Jeanette Frederiksen<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:maroon\">ERHVERVSSTYRELSEN<\/span><\/strong><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Langelinie All\u00e9 17<br>&nbsp;1780 K\u00f8benhavn \u00d8<br>&nbsp;Telefon: &#43;45 3529 1000<br>&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.erst.dk\/\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;color:black\">www.erst.dk<\/span><\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">ERHVERVS- OG V\u00c6KSTMINISTERIET<br>&nbsp;<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\">P<\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:green\">Pas p\u00e5 milj\u00f8et - udskriv kun denne e-mail hvis det er n\u00f8dvendigt<\/span><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;<\/span><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><\/body><\/html>","type":"html","stripped_images":[],"embedded_images":[],"options":{"strip-embedded":true}},"priorityId":null,"attachments":[]}

<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody><\/table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            <\/td>\r\n        <\/tr>\r\n    <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/td>\r\n                                        <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY \/\/ -->\r\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;min-width: 100%;background-color: #12171b;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bodyContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet. Lovovertr\u00e6delse kan straffes med b\u00f8de.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Med venlig hilsen&nbsp;\/Best regards<\/span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Jeanette Frederiksen<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:maroon\">ERHVERVSSTYRELSEN<\/span><\/strong><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Langelinie All\u00e9 17<br>&nbsp;1780 K\u00f8benhavn \u00d8<br>&nbsp;Telefon: &#43;45 3529 1000<br>&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.erst.dk\/\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;color:black\">www.erst.dk<\/span><\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">ERHVERVS- OG V\u00c6KSTMINISTERIET<br>&nbsp;<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\">P<\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:green\">Pas p\u00e5 milj\u00f8et - udskriv kun denne e-mail hvis det er n\u00f8dvendigt<\/span><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;<\/span><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><\/body><\/html>","type":"html","stripped_images":[],"embedded_images":[],"options":{"strip-embedded":true}},"priorityId":null,"attachments":[]}

style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">Bedste hilsner<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">Lasse Guldsborg<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">Avnholtsvej 31<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">M. <a href=\"mailto:lasse@guldsborg.dk\">lasse@guldsborg.dk<\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D;mso-fareast-language:EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Fra:<\/span><\/b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"> Virk.dk support [mailto:_support@erst.dk] <br><b>Sendt:<\/b> 15. marts 2016 13:35<br><b>Til:<\/b> Lasse Guldsborg &lt;lasse@guldsborg.dk&gt;<br><b>Emne:<\/b> Re: Robinsonliste for virksomheder? [#139351]<o:p><\/o:p><\/span><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;<\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\">--<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p>Hej Lasse<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p>Det er kun personer der kan komme p\u00e5 Robinsonlisten. For at undg\u00e5 reklamehenvendelser kan du reklamebeskytte din virksomheden.&nbsp;<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\">N\u00e5r du reklamebeskytter en virksomhed, m\u00e5 virksomhedens registrerede oplysninger fra Det Centrale Virksomhedsregister (CVR p\u00e5 Virk) ikke anvendes af andre til uopfordrede henvendelser. Andre m\u00e5 dog godt kontakte jer i reklame\u00f8jemed, hvis de finder jeres oplysninger, hvor I selv har offentliggjort dem, fx p\u00e5 jeres hjemmeside. <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\/cvr-hj%C3%A6lp\/f%C3%A5-hj%C3%A6lp-til-cvr\/reklamebeskyttelse\" target=\"_blank\">L\u00e6s mere om, hvad reklamebeskyttelse omfatter<\/a> i CVR Hj\u00e6lp.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>S\u00e5dan v\u00e6lger du reklamebeskyttelse<\/strong><br>Du kan v\u00e6lge reklamebeskyttelse, enten <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Start_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-start-virksomhed%2C\">n\u00e5r du opretter din virksomhed<\/a> eller <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">senere ved at v\u00e6lge \u2019\u00c6ndre virksomhed\u2019<\/a> p\u00e5 Virk Indberet. Hvis du v\u00e6lger '\u00c6ndre virksomhed' skal du ind under punktet 'Rediger stamdata' for at finde \u201dDer \u00f8nskes reklamebeskyttelse i CVR\u201d. Herefter skal du angive, hvilken dato \u00e6ndringerne skal g\u00e6lde fra. Du kan ogs\u00e5 reklamebeskytte P-enheder.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Stamoplysningerne er stadig offentlige<\/strong><br>Oplysningerne er <a href=\"http:\/\/datacvr.virk.dk\/data\" target=\"_blank\">fortsat offentligt tilg\u00e6ngelige<\/a> i CVR p\u00e5 Virk, men det fremg\u00e5r, at virksomheden er reklamebeskyttet. Du kan v\u00e6lge at <a href=\"https:\/\/indberet.virk.dk\/myndigheder\/stat\/ERST\/Webreg_aendre_virksomhed__lukke_virksomhed?nm_extag=Link%3D%2Cforside%2Cmest-anvendte-andre-virksomhed%2C\">fjerne dit telefonnummer og mailadresse<\/a> fra virksomhedens stamdata, s\u00e5 de ikke bliver vist i CVR p\u00e5 Virk. Adressen er obligatorisk og kan ikke fjernes.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><div><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delser til politiet<\/strong><br>Du kan anmelde overtr\u00e6delse af reglerne om reklamebeskyttelse til politiet. Lovovertr\u00e6delse kan straffes med b\u00f8de.<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-bottom:12.0pt\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Med venlig hilsen&nbsp;\/Best regards<\/span>&nbsp; &nbsp;<br>&nbsp;Jeanette Frederiksen<o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:maroon\">ERHVERVSSTYRELSEN<\/span><\/strong><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">Langelinie All\u00e9 17<br>&nbsp;1780 K\u00f8benhavn \u00d8<br>&nbsp;Telefon: &#43;45 3529 1000<br>&nbsp;<\/span><a href=\"http:\/\/www.erst.dk\/\"><span style=\"font-size:7.5pt;color:black\">www.erst.dk<\/span><\/a><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">ERHVERVS- OG V\u00c6KSTMINISTERIET<br>&nbsp;<\/span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\">P<\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:Webdings;color:green\"> <\/span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:green\">Pas p\u00e5 milj\u00f8et - udskriv kun denne e-mail hvis det er n\u00f8dvendigt<\/span><span style=\"color:black\">&nbsp;<\/span><o:p><\/o:p><\/p><\/div><\/body><\/html>","type":"html","stripped_images":[],"embedded_images":[],"options":{"strip-embedded":true}},"priorityId":null,"attachments":[]}

<\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody><\/table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            <\/td>\r\n        <\/tr>\r\n    <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/td>\r\n                                        <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY \/\/ -->\r\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;min-width: 100%;background-color: #12171b;border-top: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span <\/td>\r\n    <\/tr>\r\n<\/tbody><\/table>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n            <\/td>\r\n        <\/tr>\r\n    <\/tbody>\r\n<\/table><\/td>\r\n                                        <\/tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY \/\/ -->\r\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;min-width: 100%;background-color: #12171b;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\r\n                                        <tr>\r\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bodyContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"min-width: 100%;border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\">\r\n                    <tbody><tr>\r\n\r\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #ffffff;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\r\n\r\n                            <div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>CIRQUE DU SOLEIL - Varekai<\/strong><\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Biggest, Most Breathtaking, Most Popular Show on the Planet comes to UAE, this time with its Number &nbsp;Written and Directed by Dominic Champagne&nbsp;Varekai is a critically-acclaimed production that has wowed&nbsp;over 8 million people worldwide since it first premiered in&nbsp;Montreal in 2002. Since then, Varekai has visited more than&nbsp;72 cities in 20 different countries around the world.&nbsp;Deep within a forest, at the summit of a volcano, exists&nbsp;an extraordinary world where something else is possible.&nbsp;A world called Varekai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe sky lets go a solitary young man, and the story of Varekai&nbsp;begins. Parachuted into the shadows of a&nbsp;magical forest,&nbsp;a kaleidoscopic world imbued with fantastical creatures, a&nbsp;young man takes flight in an&nbsp;adventure both absurd and&nbsp;extraordinary. On this day at the edge of time, in this place of&nbsp;pure and&nbsp;undiluted possibility, begins an inspired incantation&nbsp;to a life rediscovered and to a newly found wonder in the&nbsp;mysteries of the world and the mind.&nbsp;The word Varekai (pronounced ver\u00b7ay\u00b7\u2019kie) means \u201cwherever\u201d&nbsp;in the Romany language of the gypsies\u2014the universal&nbsp;wanderers. Written and directed by Dominic Champagne,&nbsp;this production pays tribute to the nomadic soul, to the spirit&nbsp;and art of the circus tradition, and&nbsp;to those who quest with&nbsp;infinite passion along the path that leads to Varekai.&nbsp;Varekai emerges from an&nbsp;explosive fusion of drama and&nbsp;acrobatics. The impossible becomes possible in stunning&nbsp;displays of skill&nbsp;and power set against innovative music&nbsp;and otherworldly sets, interwoven with vivid choreography&nbsp;that&nbsp;speaks to all in the universal language of movement.&nbsp;The pendulum of time sweeps backward, paying tribute to&nbsp;the ancient and rare circus traditions of Icarian games and&nbsp;Georgian dance.&nbsp;Varekai then catapults to the future with&nbsp;revolutionary twists on such acts as Russian Swings and&nbsp;Slippery Surface.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVarekai features an international cast of 50 performers and&nbsp;musicians from 19 different countries.<\/div>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">Starting From 16 - 24 September in Dubai<\/span><\/strong>.<br>\r\nTickets go on sale ONLY &amp; EXCLUSIVELY at&nbsp;<u><strong><span
